text: Ðis sant þe landimare to Archet of eldmannes wrthe on irichte anlang hina imares to þan scamelen.
From þanne scamelen anlang hine imares oð wdebrige.
Of wudebricge, a dune anlang streames oð land scorforð.
Of þane forde, anlang leouen imare oð kinghes imare.
And gemare, oð funtemel forð of þanne forð.
Adune mid stream oþes bissopes imare ut sceoþaþ.
Þanen on irichte to þan lipgete.
From þane gete on irichte to anne wonalre.
Of þane alre, on irichte to sucgimade hauede.
Of þane hauede on irichte þurch ðene holte to Wlgares imaren.
Of þan imaren eft on eldemanneswyrde.
